{"word":"Caleb","slug":"caleb","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Caleb</b> - son of Jephunneh, General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=6'>Num 13:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=30'>Num 13:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=24'>Num 14:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=65'>Num 26:65</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=34&verse=19'>Num 34:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=14&verse=14'>Jos 14:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=14'>Jos 15:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=12'>Jos 21:12</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=15'>Jdg 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=15'>1Ch 4:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=42'>1Ch 2:42</a><p/>---Facts Concerning<p/>One of the twelve spies<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=6'>Nu 13:6</a><p/>Courageous<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=30'>Num 13:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=6'>Num 14:6-9</a><p/>Preserved when other spies perished<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=37'>Num 14:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=38'>Num 14:38</a><p/>Consecrated to God<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=36'>De 1:36</a><p/>Vigorous and faithful in old age<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=14&verse=10'>Jos 14:10-14</a><p/>Invincible, drove out the giants from his inheritance<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=14'>Jos 15:14</a>"}]}